WEBVTT

00:00:58.664 --> 00:01:00.552
He actually says people matter,

00:01:00.576 --> 00:01:04.203
and the reason they matter
is that they are incubating something:

00:01:04.227 --> 00:01:05.377
knowledge.

00:01:05.871 --> 00:01:12.514
In David's view, knowledge is a force
of almost unlimited power in the universe

00:01:12.538 --> 00:01:15.736
and also a force
that will determine our future.

00:01:15.760 --> 00:01:19.843
David Deutsch (from TEDGlobal 2005):
We can survive and we can fail to survive.

00:01:20.561 --> 00:01:23.299
But it depends, not on chance,

00:01:23.323 --> 00:01:26.989
but on whether we create
the relevant knowledge in time.

00:01:27.013 --> 00:01:30.471
The overwhelming majority
of all species and all civilizations